oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: UNICEF tour - New Zealand - 1972 - part 11
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Part eleven of a 1972 UNICEF fundraiser tour performance in New Zealand. Featuring Tex Ritter (host/performer) and Leroy Van Dyke (performer).
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Leroy Van Dyke
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: (00:00) Big Wide Wonderful World Of Country Music (Leroy Van Dyke) -- (00:49) Van Dyke thanks the audience and talks about fan support during his recording career, and introduces the next tune -- (02:52) Black Cloud (Leroy Van Dyke) -- (06:55) Van Dyke introduces the next tune -- (07:15) The Auctioneer (Leroy Van Dyke) -- (09:36) Tex Ritter praises Van Dyke and thanks the audience -- (09:57) Closing statements (Tex Ritter) -- (11:58) [Unidentified] thanks the cast -- (12:15) [Unidentified Maori song] ([Unidentified]) -- Closing statements
